# 🧾 RateMyBond — Full Codebase Explanation & Learning Roadmap

> Written for a 2nd-year student who built this with AI.
> Use this document to **understand everything that is happening** in your own project.

---

## 📁 What Did You Build?

**RateMyBond** is a full-stack-ready SaaS web application for evaluating financial bonds. Think of it like an AI-powered credit scoring tool — you input details about a bond (debt levels, cash flows, coupon rate etc.) and the app calculates an indicative rating: AAA, AA, A, BBB, BB, or Junk.

The app has:
- A **landing page** (marketing page to attract users)
- A **bond calculator** (the core product)
- A **sign-in page** (Google OAuth via Firebase)
- **Static legal pages** (Terms, Privacy, Cookies, About, Help)
- A **cookie consent banner** (GDPR-style)
- A **terms modal** (gates access to the calculator)

---

