## 🧱 The Technology Stack (and Why Each Was Used)

| Technology | What It Is | Why Used Here |
|---|---|---|
| **React 18** | JavaScript UI library | Build components and manage state |
| **Vite** | Build tool & dev server | Super-fast local development |
| **React Router v6** | Client-side routing library | Navigate between pages without page reload |
| **Tailwind CSS** | Utility-first CSS framework | Style everything using class names |
