## 🏗 PART 8 — Vite (Build Tool)

**Vite** is the modern replacement for Create React App. It makes development fast.

```js
// vite.config.js
export default defineConfig({
  base: "./",          // relative paths (for deployment)
  plugins: [react()],  // enables JSX transformation
});
```

**Key commands:**
```bash
npm run dev     # start local development server (hot reload)
npm run build   # build optimised files for production
npm run preview # preview the production build locally
```

