| `main.jsx` | App entry point | `ReactDOM.createRoot`, `BrowserRouter`, `StrictMode` |
| `App.jsx` | Root layout + routes | `Routes`, `Route`, `useState`, `useNavigate`, spread props |
| `Navbar.jsx` | Top navigation | `useState`, `Link`, responsive hamburger menu |
| `Hero.jsx` | Landing hero section | Props, event handling, Tailwind grid |
