| `TermsConsentModal.jsx` | Terms gate modal | Props, `useEffect`, controlled checkbox |
| `StaticPage.jsx` | Reusable legal pages | `Array.isArray`, conditional rendering, spread props |
| `LandingPage.jsx` | Landing page layout | Component composition |
| `SignInPage.jsx` | Google sign-in page | Firebase Auth, `useEffect`, `async/await`, `onAuthStateChanged` |
| `BondCalculatorPage.jsx` | Core product | Complex state, derived state, `reduce`, `map`, `filter` |
| `ratingModel.js` | Data + weights | Pure data, `export const`, scoring algorithm |
| `firebase.js` | Firebase setup | `initializeApp`, `getAuth`, environment variables |
| `vite.config.js` | Build configuration | `defineConfig`, Vite plugins |

